rm(list = ls())
require(data.table)
## Loading required package: data.table
require(anytime)
## Loading required package: anytime
workingdirectory = "/Users/aslierdal/Desktop/etm58D/Homework2"
setwd(workingdirectory)

# read match and odd data
matches= readRDS("df9b1196-e3cf-4cc7-9159-f236fe738215_matches.rds")
odds = readRDS("df9b1196-e3cf-4cc7-9159-f236fe738215_odd_details.rds")

# process matches data

matches = matches[,c("home","away") := tstrsplit(score,':')]
matches[,c('result') := ifelse(as.numeric(home) + as.numeric(away) > 2.5, "2", "1")]
## Warning in ifelse(as.numeric(home) + as.numeric(away) > 2.5, "2", "1"): NAs
## introduced by coercion
matches = matches[,c("matchId", "result")]


# process odd data

odds = odds[bookmaker=="Betsson" | bookmaker=="Beyway" | bookmaker=="bet-at-home" | bookmaker=="12BET" | bookmaker=="youwin"]
odds = odds[betType=='1x2' | betType=='dc' | betType=='bts' | (betType=='ou' & totalhandicap=='2.5')]


odds=odds[order(matchId,betType,oddtype,bookmaker,date)]
odds=odds[,list(final_odd=odd[.N]),by=list(matchId,oddtype,bookmaker)]
odds=dcast(odds,matchId~bookmaker+oddtype,value.var='final_odd')

odds_matches=merge(odds,matches,by='matchId')
odds_matches=odds_matches[,matchId:=NULL]
odds_matches=odds_matches[complete.cases(odds_matches)]

results = odds_matches[,'result']
odds_matches = odds_matches[, result := NULL]
